Text: Kudos for this great collection of Superman books so far. I've read almost up to the start of the New Krypton arc, and eagerly awaiting the completion of the chronology. Great work!
That's gotta be one of the most incredible torrents I ever seen! congratz pal, I hope you can continue and make a 8th pack. By the way, that's a shame there are so few seeders :(
